# APINetworkTrace - Multi-Environment Endpoint Monitor

APINetworkTrace helps monitor global or segmented API infrastructures and track real-time metrics.

## Features
- Logs response time + status code  
- Optional JSON export  
- Retry + timeout support  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/23_APINetworkTrace.git
cd 23_APINetworkTrace
python monitor.py
